00:11:23,458 --> 00:11:24,916
- [gasps]
- [Mimi and Tivey yell]

269
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,916
[rumbling]

270
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,875
- [gasping]

271
00:11:29,916 --> 00:11:31,458
[both yell]

272
00:11:31,541 --> 00:11:34,041
[chorus vocalizing]

